languages.text: "Полагаю, вам виднее. Не задумывался об этом ранее и вряд ли смогу поделиться полезным мнением, Лорд-капитан".
"I suppose you have a better idea of that than I do. It is something I have never thought about before and on which I hardly have an opinion worth sharing, Lord Captain."

languages.text: “我认为您应该比我更清楚这一点。我从来没考虑过这个问题，也没有任何有价值的意见值得分享，舰长大人。”
languages.original_text: "I suppose you have a better idea of that than I do. It is something I have never thought about before and on which I hardly have an opinion worth sharing, Lord Captain."

languages.text: "Das wisst Ihr wohl besser als ich. Ich habe noch nie darüber nachgedacht und habe gewiss keine Meinung dazu, die mitzuteilen wert wäre, Lord Captain."

languages.text: "Sanırım bu hususta benden daha bilgilisiniz. Daha önce aklımdan böyle bir şey hiç geçmemişti. Maalesef ki buna dair paylaşmaya değer pek de bir fikrim yok Lord Kaptan."
languages.original_text: "I suppose you have a better idea of that than I do. It is something I have never thought about before and on which I hardly have an opinion worth sharing, Lord Captain."
